A luxurious residential complex called Laya Residences is situated right in the middle of Jumeirah Village Circle. One of Dubai's top 10 most investigated neighbourhoods, Jumeirah Village Circle is a thriving residential region that is thriving with rising communities.

It was finished in 2017 and has convenient access to all the amenities that match the lifestyle of those who live there. It is also strategically located. There are several amenities available at Laya Residences, including a sizable leisure pool, a sauna room, a fully furnished gym, a yoga studio, a jogging track on the terrace, a seating space on the terrace, and a play area for kids. There are just 164 apartments, some of them are large studios, others are one or two bedrooms.
